Rating: 3
Its a bit hard to rate this, as I used King Arthur toasted hazelnuts instead of walnuts and the end result was a bit too dry. As others have mentioned using other nuts, I submit this as a recommendation to use more butter or even yogurt in the cake if using these hazelnuts. Texture aside, the flavour was excellent.

